BRANCH-0.6.x
============================================================================

RELEASE-0.6.18 (January 15, 2007)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*) Bugfix: wchar, wstring (reported by Elmar Rudigier)
	Added #ifdef _GLIBCXX_USE_WCHAR_T for ccmDebug methods which use wchar
	and wstring types.


RELEASE-0.6.17 (December 7, 2006)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*) Bugfix: Interix (reported by Duft Markus)
	Added _CCM_EXPORT_DECL_ Makro definition to the Makefile.py files in the 
	CCM_Local/HomeFinder and CCM_Remote/SessionContainer directory.


RELEASE-0.6.16 (November 22, 2006)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*) Refactoring: LocalComponents/CCM.h
	Added virtual destructors to all classes.
	
*) Bugfix: Interix (reported by Duft Markus)
	Added _CCM_EXPORT_DECL_ Makro to HomeFinder.h and CCMContainer.h which
	uses static attributes.
	

RELEASE-0.6.14 (September 11, 2006)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*) Bugfix: ccm/CCM_Remote/Makefile.py
 	Added optional package-name and package-version definitions.